      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "System.getProperty(&quot;user.name&quot;); no longer works on newer Windows versions (since Windows Vista), if the Java program is running as a background Service. Instead of the username &quot;SYSTEM&quot;, it returns something like &lt;Domain&gt;\\&lt;Hostname&gt;$  -- So basically it returns the hostname instead of the username.... :-)"
